{"tid":1925810,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"香港係全世界第一","createTime":"2020-03-14T15:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T13:19:45.000Z","uid":189986,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c220a4cd94d4bcf01ea9fd621b96979c1bfb96fd","tid":1925810,"uid":189986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:57:42.000Z","msg":"我正式宣布香港係全世界第一<br />\n<br />\n一開頭去到歐洲讀書，已經覺得啲車好唔密好唔方便，好多人都係以腳/單車/私家車代步<br />\n而香港，去到邊都有黨鐵，就算而家無得坐，都有巴士小巴，又可以坐渡海小輪<br />\n<br />\n去過倫敦都知，佢地鐵係冇網絡，冇網絡，係冇網絡架！真係癡撚線架！其他火車，都係過隧道收唔到，你諗吓有無試過過大老山/尖沙咀去金鐘收唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，我想講返防疫<br />\n喺隔離post唔知見到邊條傻閪話我地：真係搞笑黃皮膚喺到笑返白人，自我Racist之餘踩低自己<br />\n你諗吓香港就算中門大開，個數都Keep住100幾。而意大利日升幾千，日日死幾百，西班牙上到四千，英國都就黎1000。但我啲同學仲喺到開玩笑，覺得佢仲係just a flu, 上堂照lam手指，周圍掂，唔洗手就用手食包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見到都想死<br />\n<br />\n香港人真係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好掛住香港好想返黎。我生於香港都想死於香港"},{"pid":"24747b29fee1265b07228ed4108d07e0a424107c","tid":1925810,"uid":8500,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:59:04.000Z","msg":"屋企掃地用1分鐘就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619906b414a866cf3428dc72a45b0d97da2d6a78","tid":1925810,"uid":299938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:59:20.000Z","msg":"Agger 除咗民主"},{"pid":"299ac9caec9687dc46c63147dcd9380ff3049b7c","tid":1925810,"uid":299938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"24747b29fee1265b07228ed4108d07e0a424107c","tid":1925810,"uid":8500,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:59:04.000Z","msg":"屋企掃地用1分鐘就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T15:59:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" clas